SOURCE: https://github.com/cardanosolutions/ogmios/blob/master/docs/content/mini-protocols/local-chain-sync.md#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
    "jsonrpc": "2.0",
    "method": "findIntersection",
    "params": {
        "points": [
            {
              "slot": 39916796,
              "id": "e72579ff89dc9ed325b723a33624b596c08141c7bd573ecfff56a1f7229e4d09"
            },
            {
              "slot": 23068793,
              "id": "69c44ac1dda2ec74646e4223bc804d9126f719b1c245dadc2ad65e8de1b276d7"
