TITLE: Evaluate Transaction Request - JSON
DESCRIPTION: This JSON snippet shows the structure of a request to evaluate a transaction using Ogmios. Similar to transaction submission, the transaction is provided as a base16-encoded CBOR string. The 'method' parameter must be set to 'evaluateTransaction'. This endpoint is useful for determining script execution costs without actually submitting the transaction to the network.
SOURCE: https://github.com/cardanosolutions/ogmios/blob/master/docs/content/mini-protocols/local-tx-submission.md#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: JSON
CODE:
```
{
    "jsonrpc": "2.0",
    "method": "evaluateTransaction",
    "params": { "transaction": { "cbor": "<base16>" } }
}
```

