TITLE: Running Application with Tracers - Haskell
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates how to use the configured tracers within the application. It uses `withStdoutTracer` to set up tracers that output to standard output, passing in an empty configuration and a lambda that receives the `tracers` record.  It then runs `myHttpApplication` and `myDbApplication` concurrently, passing each the corresponding tracer.
