TITLE: Embedding Git Revision with Template Haskell
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to use the `gitRevParseHEAD` function from the `Data.Git.Revision.TH` module to embed the Git revision hash of the HEAD commit into a Haskell program at compile time. It requires the `TemplateHaskell` language extension to be enabled.
