TITLE: Cloning and building secp256k1 with Schnorr signature support
DESCRIPTION: This set of commands clones a specific revision of the bitcoin-core's secp256k1 repository, configures it with Schnorr signature support, and installs it.  It requires autoconf and libtool to be installed.
SOURCE: https://github.com/cardanosolutions/ogmios/blob/master/docs/content/getting-started/building.md#_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: console
CODE:
```
git clone https://github.com/bitcoin-core/secp256k1.git
cd secp256k1
git reset --hard ac83be33d0956faf6b7f61a60ab524ef7d6a473a
./autogen.sh
./configure --prefix=/usr --enable-module-schnorrsig --enable-experimental
make
make check
sudo make install
```

